headline: Influenza A(H1N1) - update 34
main_text: As of 06:00 GMT, 20 May 2009, 41 countries have officially reported 10 243 cases of influenza A(H1N1) infection, including 80 deaths. The breakdown of the number of laboratory-confirmed cases by country is given in the following table and map.
